'''Æthelwold''' (or '''Æthelweald'''; died 830) was a medieval [[Bishop of Lichfield]].

Æthelwald was consecrated in 818 and died in 830.<ref name=Handbook218>Fryde, et al. ''Handbook of British Chronology'' p. 218</ref>

